Good quality prints but awkward to hang My two framed prints arrived within a reasonable time. The print quality and the framing is good. My only criticism is that the only means of hanging the print is via a brass "eye" (I don't know the technical term) at the top of the frame on the reverse side. You can put a hook into it, but the hook will be partially visible. I would have preferred that a string be attached to the reverse of the frame to allow hanging.
